Details

Bank of America Plaza is a 55-story, 1.3 million square foot office tower that stands at the pinnacle of the Atlanta skyline as the tallest building in Atlanta and 125th tallest in the world. The nationally recognized office tower faces its border streets at a 45-degree angle to maximize the views to the north and south. Located on Peachtree Street, Bank of America Plaza boasts a prime location, first-class amenities, and a top-tier and tech-focused tenant roster.
